column2: select count (*) , public.ncarey.stim_timestamps.timestamp from public.ncarey.session_eeg, public.ncarey.stim_timestamps where public.ncarey.session_eeg.session_ID = # and public.ncarey.stim_timestamps.session_ID = # and public.ncarey.session_eeg.timestamp < public.ncarey.stim_timestamps.timestamp group by public.ncarey.stim_timestamps.timestamp) select stim_timestamps_index.index_value, public.ncarey.stim_timestamps.stim_ID from stim_timestamps_index, public.ncarey.stim_timestamps where public.ncarey.stim_timestamps.session_ID = # and public.ncarey.stim_timestamps.timestamp = stim_timestamps_index.timestamp order by stim_timestamps_index.index_value
